      "intent_thread_url": "https://groups.google.com/a/chromium.org/d/msgid/blink-dev/CAMtUnc7FM0-e_zdX0S0US%3DhiG5e%2B51r%3DTfjR4%3DfW-TJbqrMS9A%40mail.gmail.com",
      "announcement_url": null,
      "experiment_goals": "There are two proposals that we are going to be experimenting with:\n\n-  The IdP-Iniated API: we'll be monitoring any implementation errors that might occur as users use agentic browsing across many websites. We think we covered most cases, but we still expect many unknown unknowns to show up.\n- The potentially_approved_sites: we'll be monitoring the rate of false positives and false negatives and how users are going through them.",
      "experiment_risks": "There aren't any risks that we are anticipating when the experiment comes to an end.",
